item.title: About honey-speaks-tech.github.io
item.description: About the website honey-speaks-tech.github.io website is created using Github pages and Hugo. Hugo is a popular open-source, fast and flexible static website generator written in Go. Hugo takes a directory with content and templates and renders them into a full HTML website GitHub Pages are public webpages hosted and published through GitHub. Reference https://levelup.gitconnected.com/build-a-personal-website-with-github-pages-and-hugo-6c68592204c7
